   * The ArrayBuffer contains the UTF-8 encoded JSON.
   * ```ts
   * const snapshot = Bun.generateHeapSnapshot("v8", "arraybuffer");
   * await Bun.write("heap.heapsnapshot", snapshot);
   * ```
